# Force LF line endings on every text file in this repo so gofmt,
# go vet, and other tooling produce consistent output regardless of
# the contributor's OS. Without this, Windows checkouts pick up
# CRLF on the working tree and gofmt-check in CI fires on every
# file. Binary types are listed explicitly so git never tries to
# normalise them.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary types — preserve byte-for-byte.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.gz binary
